*Description:*

* Fixes for Swagger API reflection

1.0.4
-----

*Compatible with CE:* 2.0 2.1
*Stability:* Stable Build
*Description:*

* Fixes an incompatibility with the Buckaroo Magento Extension

1.0.3
-----

*Compatible with CE:* 2.0 2.1
